name: Float
description:
CD in full colour matte finish digipak. 
Cinematic 11 track compilation (from:  Migrations, Traces, Fields of Flowers, Precious Images and Route Planner, 
+ 2 new exclusive recordings). 


1.    Lapidarium
2.    Eiland
3.    September Colours
4.    Ears Tell Us Where We Are In Space - strings version (exclusive)
5.    Fragments of Memory
6.    Sana'a
7.    Tirza Scene
8.    Ears Tell Us Where We Are In Space
9.    Lapidarium - piano version
10.  Float (exclusive)
11.  Early Morning Light

name: Banabila & Mens 12" EP
description:
Music by Banabila & Mens. 12-inch 180 gram mixed colour solid white & silver vinyl.  A special limited luxe edition of 200 pressings.  Comes in a full colour matte outer sleeve and a full colour gloss inner sleeve. Artwork & design by Gerco de Ruijter. 
Three tracks from ZoomWorld (digital release) and one exclusive track.
All tracks were remastered by Earlabs Mastering / Jos Smolders.
Includes a bonus : ZoomWorld promo CDr in full colour carton sleeve.
